# CODEOWNERS - Defines code ownership for review requirements
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default owners for everything
*                       @maintainers

# Frontend code
/frontend/              @frontend-team @maintainers
/frontend/src/          @frontend-team

# Backend code
/backend/               @backend-team @maintainers
/backend/src/           @backend-team

# Documentation
/docs/                  @docs-team @maintainers
/README.md              @maintainers

# CI/CD and infrastructure
/.github/               @devops-team @maintainers
/Dockerfile*            @devops-team @maintainers
/docker-compose.yml     @devops-team @maintainers
/*.ps1                  @devops-team @maintainers

# Security-sensitive files
/.github/workflows/security.yml  @security-team @maintainers
/.github/dependabot.yml          @security-team @maintainers
/SECURITY.md                     @security-team @maintainers
